```
# Rust/Cargo specific
target/
Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Build artifacts
**/dist/
**/build/
**/*.o
**/*.obj
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.so
**/*.a
**/*.out

# IDE/Editor files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*.tmp

# Logs
**/*.log

# Coverage
**/coverage/
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage

# Python related (if any Python in project)
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/

# System files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
```